items.description: Instructions on how to get price details from the user
items.name: get_price
items.prompt:
Get the price details from the user.
The user can give in any format and it can like 1000 rupees, 1000 INR etc..
Extract only the numerical data from it. Make sure you convert the result into integer.

items.description: Instructions on how to get rating details from the user
items.name: get_rating
items.prompt:
Get the rating details from the user.
Consider the rating system to be 5 star rating system. Ask user how many stars out of 5 stars.
Extract only the numerical data from it. Convert the result number into a scale of 0 to 100.
Example, for a 2.5 star rating the result number should be 50.
